These are Puzzles for 4x3 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-1::.
The people have 3 different jobs:  manager, writer, dressmaker
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: prince, pall-mall, blend
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, sudoku, woodworking
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: blues, folk, reggae
1. the pall-mall-smoker is the writer##1
2. the fan of reggae is on the far left##1
3. the dressmaker is on the left of the fan of blues##1
4. the person who's hobby is chess is the blend-smoker##1
5. the prince-smoker is in the middle##1
6. the dressmaker is the blend-smoker##1
7. the person who's hobby is woodworking is in the middle##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2      |     3     |
| Job      | dressmaker  | manager       | writer   |
| Cigar          | blend | prince | pall-mall |
| Hobby         | chess  | woodworking | sudoku    |
| Music-Genre   | reggae | blues       | folk      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-2::.
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: comedy, sports, scientific
The people have 3 different hobbies: rock-climbing, singing, traveling
The people have 3 different jobs:  teacher, lawyer, analyst
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, rat, snake
1. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching sports movies##1
2. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the lawyer##1
4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
5. the owner of the snake is on the far left##1
6. the owner of the snake is the teacher##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |       3       |
| Movie-Genre          | comedy      | sports  | scientific        |
| Hobby         | traveling | singing | rock-climbing |
| Job   | teacher | lawyer | analyst       |
| Pet           | snake     | rat     | hedgehog      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-3::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, coffee, mirinda
The people have 3 different jobs:  chef, dancer, software-developer
There 3 different types of food: watermelon, grapefruit, peach
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: september, june, november
1. the software-developer is the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is on the right of the person drinking almond-milk##1
3. the dancer is on the left of the person who's birthday is in september##1
4. the person eating peach is in the middle##1
5. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the software-developer##1
6. the person drinking mirinda is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |         2          |    3    |
| Beverage      | coffee    | almond-milk        | mirinda |
| Job           | dancer    | software-developer | chef    |
| Food   | watermelon | peach             | grapefruit  |
| Birthday     | november     | september                | june  |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-4::.
House: townhouse, gothic-revival, victorian
The people have 3 different jobs:  analyst, fisherman, lawyer
3 different pets are kept: hedgehog, chinchilla, turtle
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, punk, rock
1. the fan of rock is on the right of the fan of punk##1
2. the victorian house is on the left of the fisherman##1
3. the fan of classical is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
4. the townhouse house is the fan of rock##1
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the analyst##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |    2    |     3     |
| House          | gothic-revival    | victorian  | townhouse      |
| Job           | lawyer    | analyst | fisherman |
| Pet   | turtle   | chinchilla  | hedgehog     |
| Music-Genre   | classical | punk    | rock      |

