.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-5::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, singing, video-games
There are 3 different nationalities: malaysian, indonesian, chinese
There 3 different types of food: asparagus, cucumber, apple
3 different pets are kept: dog, hedgehog, lizard
1. the person eating asparagus is the indonesian##1
2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##1
3. the chinese is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the far left##1
5. the owner of the dog is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
6. the person eating apple is the malaysian##1
7. the indonesian is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |     3     |
| Hobby         | video-games | cooking     | singing   |
| Nationality           | chinese       | indonesian   | malaysian     |
| Food   | cucumber     | asparagus | apple |
| Pet           | lizard      | dog         | hedgehog  |

