.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-6::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: dahlia, marigold, lily
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: gospel, house, indie
There are 3 different favourite beverages: sprite, tea, almond-milk
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: sailing, snowboarding, tennis
1. the person who growslily is on the right of the fan of gospel##1
2. the person drinking sprite is in the middle##1
3. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
4. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who's sport is tennis##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |    3    |
| Flower          | dahlia | marigold       | lily |
| Music-Genre   | indie     | gospel       | house   |
| Beverage           | tea      | sprite       | almond-milk     |
| Sport         | sailing   | snowboarding | tennis  |

