3. the owner of the ferret is on the right of the person watching horror movies##1
4. the swisher-smoker is on the right of the fan of funk##1
5. the fan of pop is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2        |     3      |
| Cigar          | dannemann       | fonseca         | swisher   |
| Pet           | goat | ferret | goldfish |
| Movie-Genre   | horror     | mystery        | spy        |
