.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-9::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: chess, cooking, writing
There 3 different types of food: artichoke, corn, spinach
3 different pets are kept: goat, goldfish, guinea-pig
There are 3 different favourite beverages: tea, lemonade, cola
1. the person drinking cola is in the middle##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the far right##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is the person drinking lemonade##1
4. the person eating artichoke is the owner of the guinea-pig##1
5. the person eating spinach is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is writing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |         1          |     2      |    3     |
| Hobby       | cooking            | chess      | writing  |
| Food         | spinach | artichoke | corn |
| Pet         | goat               | guinea-pig | goldfish |
| Beverage   | lemonade             | cola       | tea      |

