3. the wooden house is on the right of the palace house##1
4. the electrician is on the far right##1
5. the chef is on the left of the person drinking fanta##1
6. the person drinking water is on the left of the person watching mystery movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2       |      3      |
| Job           | scientist | chef         | electrician |
