.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-11::.
3 different games are played: poker, bridge, canasta
The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: drama, horror, spy
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, french, thai
City: miami, boston, venice
1. the thai is on the right of the person playing bridge##1
2. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person watching spy movies##1
3. the person playing canasta is on the right of the person traveling to venice##1
4. the person traveling to boston is on the left of the dutch##1
5. the dutch is on the right of the person playing canasta##1
6. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person watching drama movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |     3     |
| Game           | bridge | canasta | poker |
| Movie-Genre   | spy        | horror       | drama     |
| Nationality   | french     | thai         | dutch     |
| City     | venice | boston          | miami      |

