.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-13::.
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, rock-climbing, writing
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, blue, ebony
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: dubstep, metal, punk
3 different pets are kept: snake, cat, goldfish
1. the owner of the goldfish is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the fan of punk is on the left of the owner of the snake##1
3. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the left of the fan of punk##1
4. the person who's hobby is writing is the person who likes blue##1
5. the fan of punk is on the left of the fan of dubstep##1
6. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3     |
| Hobby         | rock-climbing | cooking | writing   |
| Color           | ebony     | purple    | blue   |
| Music-Genre   | metal         | punk    | dubstep   |
| Pet         | cat       | goldfish | snake |

