The people perfer 3 different movie-genres: sports, action, superhero
The people have 3 different hobbies: collecting, sudoku, traveling
The people use 3 different means of transport: airplane, bus, motorbike
1. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##1
2. the mechanic is the person who's hobby is collecting##1
3. the person watching superhero movies is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1
4. the software-developer is on the left of the person watching action movies##1
5. the project-manager is the person driving the motorbike##1
6. the person driving the bus is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2      |     3      |
| Job    | software-developer | mechanic     | project-manager      |
| Movie-Genre        | sports | action       | superhero |
| Hobby       | sudoku | collecting | traveling  |
| Transport   | bus    | airplane   | motorbike  |

