2. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person eating mango##1
3. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
4. the owner of the chinchilla is on the far right##1
5. the teacher is on the left of the person who growsbegonia##1
6. the person eating peas is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |    3    |
| Flower      | bellflower      | orchid    | begonia    |
