3. the designer is on the left of the person who likes lavender##1
4. the person who likes lavender is on the right of the person eating strawberry##1
5. the russian is on the right of the person who likes red##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |    3    |
| Job      | accountant  | designer   | project-manager  |
| Food          | pumpkin   | strawberry | peach   |
| Color   | mauve      | red      | lavender    |
| Nationality   | pakistani | british    | russian |

