The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, bellflower, azalea
3 different pets are kept: ferret, pony, horse
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: rugby, water-polo, weightlifting
1. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person who growsazalea is on the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
3. the person drinking tea is the person who's sport is rugby##1
4. the owner of the pony is the person drinking juice##1
5. the person who growsbellflower is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
6. the person who's sport is weightlifting is on the left of the owner of the horse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |     3      |
| Beverage      | juice         | tea     | coffee     |
| Flower           | bellflower        | azalea | tulip |
| Pet   | pony        | horse   | ferret    |
| Sport         | weightlifting | rugby   | water-polo |

