.:: Puzzle 4x3-Level-1-20::.
There 3 different types of food: avocado, potato, tomato
City: nizza, new-york, paris
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: classical, folk, r&b
House: ranch-style, cape-cod, farmhouse
1. the person eating tomato is on the far left##1
2. the person traveling to paris is on the left of the person eating avocado##1
3. the fan of r&b is on the right of the cape-cod house##1
4. the ranch-style house is on the far left##1
5. the cape-cod house is in the middle##1
6. the person traveling to nizza is on the left of the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |     3      |
| Food          | tomato     | potato    | avocado    |
| City         | nizza | paris | new-york     |
| Music-Genre   | classical  | folk      | r&b        |
| House         | ranch-style   | cape-cod   | farmhouse |

 